data.description: This single story and open concept 4 bedroom, 3 bath floor plan is a great one!  The front of the house 2nd master is great for children or house guests.  All bedrooms feature walk-in closets.  The community includes amenities such as a park, rec center, common green space, nature trails and a lake.  The washer/dryer and fridge are negotiable.  Call today to schedule your private showing!!
